NAVIGATION

In order to save space, it appears on the left side of the app. On small devices it saves place by being on the bottom line and increases usability.

Main purpose is the global navigation with following functionality:
    1. Home (further as Dashboard)
    2. Finances
    3. History
    4. Schedule
    5. Documents
    6. Settings
(For more details about pages, see pages.cmd)

Alongside with navigation links, it has the Account info and access the the Profile.


